sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant CF as CF Edge
    participant Worker
    participant Axum as axum
    participant SSR as Leptos SSR
    participant D1

    Note over Browser,D1: First Visit — Server-Side Render

    Browser->>CF: GET /
    CF->>Worker: Route request
    Worker->>Axum: Forward request
    Axum->>SSR: Render route
    SSR->>D1: Fetch initial data
    D1-->>SSR: Rows
    SSR-->>Axum: Rendered HTML
    Axum-->>Worker: Response
    Worker-->>CF: Response
    CF-->>Browser: HTML + asset links

    Note over Browser: Paint (HTML visible)

    Browser->>CF: GET /pkg/app.wasm
    CF-->>Browser: WASM bundle
    Browser->>Browser: hydrate() — app becomes interactive

    Note over Browser,D1: Server Function Call

    Browser->>Worker: HTTP POST /api/server-fn (JSON)
    Worker->>D1: Query / mutation
    D1-->>Worker: Result
    Worker-->>Browser: JSON response
